    <arm_group_label>Optimization phase</arm_group_label>
    <description>The first five patients will be included for the optimization of the MRI sequences. This is to ensure that a standard protocol will work for different sizes of AAA. These patients will only be scanned once.</description>
  </arm_group>
  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Study phase</arm_group_label>
    <description>This phase will commence after the optimization phase. This phase is where we want to assess the feasibility, reproducibility and association with disease severity between MRI parameters and AAA.
